Package com.tiyb.tev.xml

This package contains classes related to the parsing of XML documents.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BlogXmlReader
    This class is responsible for parsing the XML file exported from Tumblr for a user's blogs.
    ConversationXmlReader
    This class is responsible for reading in an XML export from Tumblr containing conversations.
    ConversationXmlReader.MessageSuperStructure
    Helper class (essentially a struct), returned from the getMessages() method, which needs to return more complicated data than just the list of messages - it also needs to determine the participant ID
    ConversationXmlReader.Participant
    Helper class (essentially a struct), used for working with participant information.
    TEVXmlReader
    Super-class used by all XML-reading classes of the application, to reduce redundant code.

Package com.tiyb.tev.xml Description

This package contains classes related to the parsing of XML documents.
